    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>【INTRODUCTION】</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本作品是由数个故事的多个角色组成的视觉小说游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>【STORY】</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >曾经的这个世界，有着众多的国家，不同的习俗与信仰引发冲突，带来了永无休止的战争。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >千年前的这片大陆，生灵涂炭，赤地千里。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >直到有一天，意想不到的状况改变了这个世界。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >传说中，诺法尼亚王国听从神的教诲，获得了名为魔法的力量。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >利用压倒性的实力，诺法尼亚王国结束了长久以来的战乱，得到了世界的绝对支配权。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >魔法的存在让很多事情变得简单，各行各业飞速发展，原本数十年才能发生的改变只需要短短数月。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >依靠着魔法的力量，人们轻易就能过上富足的生活。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不再有贫穷与饥饿，不再有仇恨与战争，一个美好的新世界诞生了。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >直到，末日的降临。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >终焉的冰雪，亦是命运对这个世界的死亡判决……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >故事的旅途，也由此开始。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>【CHARACTER】</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1823890/extras/3715a5ac5bee7853c5b1edf9570750c9.avif?t=1752763013\" width=600 height=276 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1823890/extras/6dbaa2e1fcb8b0937dcd6c472d498267.avif?t=1752763013\" width=600 height=276 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1823890/extras/c8ab7aad3bf943f4b663418c452442de.avif?t=1752763013\" width=600 height=276 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1823890/extras/1c13030e00cbe18b5905dbef78d9b27e.avif?t=1752763013\" width=600 height=276 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1823890/extras/9e9c18086e904ed1e7a088d4f15aee92.avif?t=1752763013\" width=600 height=276 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1823890/extras/e95c40f6177771c5991ef4616efa5d13.avif?t=1752763013\" width=600 height=276 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>【FEATURE】</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本作品是由【吟暮篇】【咏夜篇】【奏晓篇】【始颂篇】【星鸣篇】【终叹篇】六篇故事组成。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每篇故事在相同的世界中展开，但每一篇都聚焦于不同的主角。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1823890/extras/f8fd883f64889ec289eeee9315886460.avif?t=1752763013\" width=600 height=393 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>【STAFF】</strong></p>",
